<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.187200>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Left tegmina, Scale: 10 mm. A, S. grandis, adult female; B, Phyllophorella queenslandica Rentz, Su, Ueshima sp. nov., paratopotypes, adult male; C, P. queenslandica Rentz, Su, Ueshima sp. nov., adult male, Bamaga, Qld." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/187200/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.187199>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. A, Holotype female, Siliquofera grandis Blanchard, (MHNP). B, pronotum of same, dorsal view.; B, S. grandis, adult male, Bulolo, Papua New Guinea, head and pronotum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/187199/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.187201>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Siliquofera grandis Blanchard, dorsal view, end of abdomen, male Bulolo, Papua New Guinea." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/187201/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.187202>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Siliquofera grandis Blanchard, male, Bulolo, Papua New Guinea. A, posterior view, end of abdomen, note supra-anal plate, minute spines on adjacent paraprocts and elongate cerci; B, subgenital plate, dorsal view; C, subgenital plate, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/187202/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

